Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Inflation fears
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brvn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Apr 1978
Americans believe inflation is the worst problem facing America. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.